## AutoResearch Mode

This workspace is running an autonomous research session.

Read `.autoresearch/program.md` and follow the experiment loop exactly.

Rules:
- Work with --auto high autonomy: modify files and execute commands freely
- Only modify files listed in the target section of program.md
- Record every experiment result to the journal
- If metrics improve: keep the commit (git commit)
- If no improvement: revert with git reset --hard HEAD~1
- If crash: log it in journal, revert, try next idea
- Never stop until success criteria met or manually interrupted
